        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>9800 Model vehicles built between February 26, 1996 and June 26, 1997 could experience short life
                    of the engine air cleaner element.
                </para>
                <para>This Authorized Field Change provides a parts and service procedure to improve the separation of
                    water from the engine air intake system.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
